metadata.title: Which RH850 F1Kx series have ethernet AVB?

sections.content:
Question:
Which RH850 F1Kx series have ethernet AVB?
Answer:
The RH850 F1KM-S4 and F1KH-D8 series have ethernet AVB. There are 2 ethernet AVB connections on the F1KH-D8.

RH850/F1x
